{"tid":1491532,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請不要以欺凌方式對待狗隻兒女","createTime":"2019-08-20T12:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:50:40.000Z","uid":135158,"like":17,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"37723fe78a6d2cfba02065de68c8caefdc1f8283","tid":1491532,"uid":135158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當然佢本身同佢老豆一樣仆街就當我冇講過啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上呢次運動都有唔少手足嘅父母/親戚都係狗，證明有其父唔一定有其子，分分鐘比你地欺凌嗰個都有份出黎發夢，佢地屋企受完氣番到學校比番自己友杯葛，屌你係人都心灰啦仲邊肯支持你啦<br />\n<br />\n而家開學要做第一件事係全力拉攏所有嘅中間派/淺藍/政治冷感，令佢地會去支持我地，欺凌威力係大，但會令到佢地永世同我地分割，更甚者立志當差報復<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因此，所有無法響應罷課嘅同學應把握呢個機會做盡一切文宣工作，務求未來反共嘅意志可以生生不息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStep 1: 班group share連登post, 蘋果新聞<br />\nStep 2: secret帶領輿論風向<br />\nStep 3: 校外/內派發文宣<br />\nStep 4: 學生自發於校內集會<br />\nStep 5: 全校罷課<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Final: 全港罷課+18區集會</span></span>"},{"pid":"e034b3b6a19334b54fb18a93652eba965b63ac48","tid":1491532,"uid":159596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ab6f78ba58166702f87c6087bf1529b794b516c","tid":1491532,"uid":52194,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n連坐法唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f668c95a2762e1339284e8bcef6394fd1ed70ba","tid":1491532,"uid":30837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:53:54.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af796058dbd0f20d3b3bc01ee99b7c7a617440c","tid":1491532,"uid":135158,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你毛澤東都識搵仔女批鬥父母啦，說好的拉一派打一派呢</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7d95cf990e20919a4ba3911ac665ff426347